Introduction

Mai is a Japanese dancer and singer under WAKEONE.

In 2024, she was a contestant on Mnet's survival show I-LAND2: N/a, where she ended up ranking 7th place in the final with 289,062 votes, but was chosen as the 6th member by the producers, thus securing her spot as a member of the final group, izna.

Mai made her debut with the group on November 25, 2024, with the release of their first mini album titled "N/a".
